{"tid":1306010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超知作運動 大家一齊舉報違例泊車","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T06:00:10.000Z","uid":125150,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bccf1af0226f436f133d151f706c22171b9255","tid":1306010,"uid":125150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"既然前線警員咁唔願意做野<br />\n我地作為良好市民係時候要幫下手<br />\n以違泊做例子<br />\n打1823好多時候比打999好<br />\n1823可以選擇比唔比個人資料警察回覆<br />\n你係可以選擇唔比 要佢地經1823回覆<br />\n另外 無論你打999定1823 都記住拎個投訴/報案編號<br />\n確保佢地有開檔案<br />\n<br />\n記住打1823投訴違泊 <br />\n但唔比警察直接覆 要經1823覆<br />\n咁警察就一定要開編號做野<br />\n現場等超過7分鐘唔見人<br />\n再打去1823投訴 7分鐘唔見警察<br />\n再開多個號碼 要1823再覆<br />\n大家一齊超合作運動<br />\n<br />\n同雲海之前教個差唔多<br />\n不過唔係打999 而係打1823<br />\n999試過hea鳩我 1823因爲唔同部門<br />\n就算差佬想唔做野都難啲<br />\n而家再簡短打一次比大家睇"},{"pid":"68840ad41d1027bca64653506083bc787d0e6768","tid":1306010,"uid":263464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=6dceecd1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=adf657d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">6.12一周月行動</span> - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=2cdc9a45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n7.13 - 全民中銀撳錢 - <a href=\"https://t.me/loveB